{
  "version": "1.0",
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "step1_welcome",
      "title": "欢迎使用 Pulsar",
      "description": "Pulsar 是一个基于肌肉记忆的快速启动器\n让我们用 30 秒了解核心功能\n\n核心特性：\n• 全局热键触发，无需鼠标\n• 两种模式：切换窗口 & 执行命令\n• 空间定位，盲操作友好",
      "type": "Instruction",
      "focusMode": "AlwaysFocused",
      "layout": {
        "cardPosition": "Center",
        "cardSizeMode": "Fixed",
        "fixedCardWidth": 500,
        "fixedCardHeight": 400
      },
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "ButtonClick"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "step2_open_settings",
      "title": "打开设置界面",
      "description": "请左键单击任务栏托盘中的 Pulsar 图标\n（或右键选择\"设置\"）\n\n💡 提示：托盘图标通常在屏幕右下角",
      "type": "WaitForAction",
      "focusMode": "AlwaysObserving",
      "target": {
        "type": "TrayIcon"
      },
      "layout": {
        "cardPosition": "BottomRight",
        "cardSizeMode": "Auto"
      },
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "WindowOpened",
        "targetValue": "SettingsWindow"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "step3_settings_overview",
      "title": "设置界面导览",
      "description": "这里可以配置 Pulsar 的所有功能：\n\n• 常规 - 热键、主题、启动项\n• 槽位配置 - 为不同应用配置快捷操作\n• 插件 - 管理功能扩展\n\n每个 Profile 可配置不同的槽位：\n• 通过顶部下拉框切换 Profile\n• 每个 Profile 的槽位独立配置",
      "type": "Instruction",
      "focusMode": "AlwaysObserving",
      "target": {
        "type": "Window",
        "elementName": "SettingsWindow"
      },
      "layout": {
        "targetWindow": {
          "left": 0.25,
          "top": 0.15,
          "width": 0.5,
          "height": 0.7,
          "isRelative": true
        },
        "cardPosition": "TopRight",
        "cardSizeMode": "Fixed",
        "fixedCardWidth": 450,
        "fixedCardHeight": 300
      },
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "ButtonClick"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "step4_navigate_slots",
      "title": "进入槽位配置",
      "description": "点击左侧导航栏的\"槽位配置\"选项\n\n这里可以为每个 Profile 配置专属的快捷操作",
      "type": "WaitForAction",
      "focusMode": "AlwaysObserving",
      "layout": {
        "cardPosition": "TopRight",
        "cardSizeMode": "Fixed",
        "fixedCardWidth": 450,
        "fixedCardHeight": 250
      },
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "NavigationItemClicked",
        "targetValue": "Slots"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "step5_add_slot",
      "title": "添加第一个槽位",
      "description": "点击\"添加槽位\"按钮\n\n槽位是 Pulsar 的核心概念：\n• 每个槽位对应一个快捷操作\n• 通过方向键选择槽位\n• 支持窗口切换、命令执行等多种功能",
      "type": "WaitForAction",
      "focusMode": "AlwaysObserving",
      "layout": {
        "cardPosition": "TopRight",
        "cardSizeMode": "Fixed",
        "fixedCardWidth": 450,
        "fixedCardHeight": 300
      },
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "SlotAdded",
        "targetValue": "{\"pluginId\":\"com.pulsar.winswitcher\"}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "step6_test_hotkey",
      "title": "测试热键",
      "description": "现在按下 Ctrl+Q 试试！\n\n你应该会看到轮盘菜单出现\n• 使用方向键选择槽位\n• 松开 Ctrl 键执行操作\n\n💡 提示：这是任务模式，用于快速切换窗口",
      "type": "WaitForAction",
      "focusMode": "AlwaysObserving",
      "layout": {
        "cardPosition": "TopRight",
        "cardSizeMode": "Fixed",
        "fixedCardWidth": 450,
        "fixedCardHeight": 300
      },
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "RadialMenuShown",
        "targetValue": "Task"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "step7_action_mode",
      "title": "动作模式",
      "description": "Pulsar 还有第二种模式：动作模式\n\n按下 Ctrl+Shift+Q 可以触发动作模式：\n• 执行应用专属命令\n• 运行 VBA 脚本\n• 触发自定义操作\n\n两种模式配合使用，效率翻倍！",
      "type": "Instruction",
      "focusMode": "AlwaysObserving",
      "layout": {
        "cardPosition": "TopRight",
        "cardSizeMode": "Fixed",
        "fixedCardWidth": 450,
        "fixedCardHeight": 350
      },
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "ButtonClick"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "step8_profile_system",
      "title": "Profile 系统",
      "description": "Pulsar 支持多 Profile 配置：\n\n• Global Profile - 全局可用\n• 应用专属 Profile - 自动切换\n  例如：notepad.exe、chrome.exe\n\n当你切换到不同应用时，Pulsar 会自动加载对应的 Profile 配置\n\n💡 提示：在设置界面顶部可以切换和管理 Profile",
      "type": "Instruction",
      "focusMode": "AlwaysObserving",
      "layout": {
        "cardPosition": "TopRight",
        "cardSizeMode": "Fixed",
        "fixedCardWidth": 450,
        "fixedCardHeight": 400
      },
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "ButtonClick"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "step9_complete",
      "title": "教程完成！",
      "description": "恭喜！你已经掌握了 Pulsar 的核心功能\n\n接下来你可以：\n• 为常用应用添加更多槽位\n• 探索插件系统，扩展功能\n• 自定义热键和主题\n\n开始享受高效的工作流程吧！\n\n💡 提示：随时可以在设置中重新查看教程",
      "type": "Instruction",
      "focusMode": "AlwaysFocused",
      "layout": {
        "cardPosition": "Center",
        "cardSizeMode": "Fixed",
        "fixedCardWidth": 500,
        "fixedCardHeight": 450
      },
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "ButtonClick"
      }
    }
  ]
}
